--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 01c2cf2a4b2c62142a7668242814b230, type: 3}
  m_Name: TextConfig.CharacterDescs
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  category: CharacterDescs
  textDataList:
  - id: ch_0001_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Seiras is described as an introverted, quiet character but extremely
        intelligent and agile. However, because of that introversion, he has very
        few, almost no friends, gradually isolating himself and losing confidence
        in expressing himself
    - language: 1
      text: "Seiras l\xE0 m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi h\u01B0\u1EDBng n\u1ED9i, tr\u1EA7m
        l\u1EB7ng nh\u01B0ng c\u1EF1c k\u1EF3 th\xF4ng minh v\xE0 nhanh nh\u1EB9n.
        Tuy nhi\xEAn, v\xEC t\xEDnh c\xE1ch h\u01B0\u1EDBng n\u1ED9i \u0111\xF3,
        c\u1EADu \u1EA5y c\xF3 r\u1EA5t \xEDt, g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng c\xF3 b\u1EA1n
        b\xE8, d\u1EA7n d\u1EA7n t\u1EF1 c\xF4 l\u1EADp b\u1EA3n th\xE2n v\xE0 m\u1EA5t
        t\u1EF1 tin trong vi\u1EC7c th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n b\u1EA3n th\xE2n"
  - id: ch_0002_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Tauroused is an active, lively, and very mischievous spirit beast. However,
        carrying an explosive source of energy, he cannot control it. During a training
        session, Tauroused broke many tools, leading to severe reprimands and nearly
        being expelled from the academy
    - language: 1
      text: "Tauroused l\xE0 m\u1ED9t linh th\xFA n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ED9ng, ho\u1EA1t
        b\xE1t v\xE0 r\u1EA5t ngh\u1ECBch ng\u1EE3m. Tuy nhi\xEAn, mang trong m\xECnh
        ngu\u1ED3n n\u0103ng l\u01B0\u1EE3ng b\xF9ng n\u1ED5, n\xF3 kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3
        ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. Trong m\u1ED9t bu\u1ED5i hu\u1EA5n
        luy\u1EC7n, Tauroused \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m h\u1ECFng nhi\u1EC1u d\u1EE5ng c\u1EE5,
        d\u1EABn \u0111\u1EBFn b\u1ECB khi\u1EC3n tr\xE1ch n\u1EB7ng n\u1EC1 v\xE0
        su\xFDt b\u1ECB \u0111u\u1ED5i kh\u1ECFi h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n"
  - id: ch_0003_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Sakura is a spirit with wings like a cherry blossom in full spring bloom.
        With a radiant appearance and a beautiful face, she becomes the center of
        attention wherever she appears. She is an extremely upright and straightforward
        girl, so much so that those around her feel uncomfortable, leading to her
        being disliked and avoided
    - language: 1
      text: "Sakura l\xE0 m\u1ED9t tinh linh c\xF3 \u0111\xF4i c\xE1nh gi\u1ED1ng
        nh\u01B0 hoa anh \u0111\xE0o n\u1EDF r\u1ED9 v\xE0o m\xF9a xu\xE2n. V\u1EDBi
        v\u1EBB ngo\xE0i r\u1EA1ng r\u1EE1 v\xE0 khu\xF4n m\u1EB7t xinh \u0111\u1EB9p,
        c\xF4 \u1EA5y lu\xF4n tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh t\xE2m \u0111i\u1EC3m ch\xFA \xFD
        b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 n\u01A1i n\xE0o c\xF4 xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n. C\xF4 \u1EA5y
        l\xE0 m\u1ED9t c\xF4 g\xE1i c\u1EF1c k\u1EF3 ch\xEDnh tr\u1EF1c v\xE0 th\u1EB3ng
        th\u1EAFn, \u0111\u1EBFn n\u1ED7i nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi xung quanh c\u1EA3m
        th\u1EA5y kh\xF3 ch\u1ECBu, d\u1EABn \u0111\u1EBFn vi\u1EC7c c\xF4 b\u1ECB
        gh\xE9t b\u1ECF v\xE0 xa l\xE1nh"
